%% Data Flow Diagram: llm-d Inference Scheduler
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (ext-proc)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sidecar as P/D Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prefill as Prefill Worker<br/>vLLM Pod
    participant Decode as Local Decode vLLM<br/>8001/TCP
    participant ZMQ as vLLM KV-Events<br/>5556/TCP ZMQ

    Note over Client,ZMQ: Flow 1: Standard Inference (Non-Disaggregated)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Gateway->>EPP: gRPC ext-proc request<br/>9002/TCP plaintext
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool/Pods<br/>443/TCP TLS, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: Pod endpoints
    Note over EPP: Filter & Score candidates<br/>(load-aware, session-affinity,<br/>prefix-cache, etc.)
    EPP-->>Gateway: Selected endpoint<br/>gRPC response
    Gateway->>Decode: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
    Decode-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,ZMQ: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (P/D)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Gateway->>EPP: gRPC ext-proc request<br/>9002/TCP plaintext
    Note over EPP: P/D profile handler selects<br/>prefill + decode targets
    EPP-->>Gateway: Routing decision with<br/>x-prefiller-host-port header
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward to decode worker<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000/TCP
    Note over Sidecar: Validate prefill target<br/>against SSRF allowlist
    Sidecar->>Prefill: Prefill request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS 1.2+ optional
    Prefill-->>Sidecar: KV transfer params response
    Sidecar->>Decode: Decode request with KV params<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8001/TCP
    Note over Decode,Prefill: KV-cache transfer<br/>(NIXL v2 / shared-storage / SGLang)
    Decode-->>Sidecar: Inference response (streaming)
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON/SSE Response

    Note over Client,ZMQ: Flow 3: KV-Cache Event Subscription

    ZMQ->>EPP: ZMQ PUB/SUB<br/>5556/TCP plaintext
    Note over EPP: Update precise prefix<br/>cache scorer state
